snippet.title: Adarna Trailer
snippet.description:
Senshi.Labs' next educational game. Coming soon.

From the corrido written by José de la Cruz, comes a turn-based role-playing game adaptation.

Core Team:
Mark Detroit Tañeca (Designer, World Creator)
Jon Adam Reyes (Lead Writer)
Eunice Grace Gatdula (Artist)
Neil Alcuran (Lead QA)
Erin Yap (QA)
Sheryl Lim (QA)
Arvin Cabang (Editor)
Doc B (Producer, Assistant Writer/Editor, QA)

Update: The game has been released March 7, 2015: http://senshi.ph/2015/03/adarna/
